<div id="assessment">
  <div class="assessment-inner">


    <section>
      <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-8 mx-auto">

            <div class="card text-dark mb-2">

                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h1>
                        {{title}}</h1>
                    <hr>


                            <h4 class="card-title">Typing Speed Test</h4>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                This sections seeks to address your typing speed as well as accuracy under certain conditions. A paragraph is given below for you to rewrite.
                                Let us see how many "correct words" from the passage you can obtain within a one minute period.
                            </p>
                            <div id="countdown">
                                Time Remaining:
                                <span id="timer">01:00</span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <textarea disabled id="testingParagraph" style="overflow:hidden; height: 120px;" readonly> I challenged myself this year to be more adventurous and try my very best to step out of my comfort zone. I realized that this even happened without most of my input, curved balls were just thrown everywhere and luckily I was getting myself mentally prepared for this. The most yearned for and long awaited break named SUMMER was finally here and that meant many stuff for me.
                                </textarea>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <input id="hiddenParagraph" readonly value="I challenged myself this year to be more adventurous and try my very best to step out of my comfort zone. I realized that this even happened without most of my input, curved balls were just thrown everywhere and luckily I was getting myself mentally prepared for this. The most yearned for and long awaited break named SUMMER was finally here and that meant many stuff for me. ">
                                </input>

                            </div>
                            <div style="hidden">
                                <input type="textbox" id="userInput" placeholder="Type here..." onkeypress="textComparison(event)" onpaste="return false" />
                            </div>
                            <div style="text-align: center">
                                <button id="startBtn" class="btn btn-success btn-color" onclick="startTimer()">Click to Start</button>
                            </div>
                            <br>
                            <div class="progress" style="height: 20px">
                                <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped progress-bar-animated progress-bar-gold" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="95"
                                    aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: 95%">95%</div>
                            </div>
                            <div style="text-align: center">
                                <span>
                                    <form action="/assessment/typing" method="POST">
                                        <input name="wpm" id="wpm" value="" />
                                        <button type="submit" id="nextBtn" class="btn btn-primary mt-5 btn-color" disabled>Save and Continue</button>
                                    </form>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</section>
</div>
</div>
